{"tid":2511333,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議港府實施空置稅","createTime":"2021-04-30T23:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T23:45:00.000Z","uid":325838,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"72a6ceec090a12de4cadc608d45117662fcbbe29","tid":2511333,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:21:12.000Z","msg":"中央已開聲要房住不炒<br />\n港府應當不停步推行打擊炒樓政策<br />\n由少至多推行空置稅正是必須的<br />\n<br />\n差估署：去年空置私樓高達5.23萬伙　大埔區冠絕全港空置率11%<br />\n<br />\n差估署今日（30日）公布《香港物業報告2021》的完整版本，數字顯示，截至去年底，整體住宅空置率按年升0.6個百分點至4.3%，涉及空置物業多達52,366伙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/619276/%E5%B7%AE%E4%BC%B0%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E9%AB%98%E9%81%945-23%E8%90%AC%E4%BC%99-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%8D%80%E5%86%A0%E7%B5%95%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%8711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F619276%2F%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%25A7%2581%25E6%25A8%2593%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2581%25945-23%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BC%2599-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%258E%258711&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=c338abc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/619276/%E5%B7%AE%E4%BC%B0%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E9%AB%98%E9%81%945-23%E8%90%AC%E4%BC%99-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%8D%80%E5%86%A0%E7%B5%95%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%8711</a>"},{"pid":"33d152d94a2c08b466061249f77146867d2f6fee","tid":2511333,"uid":325838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:25:22.000Z","msg":"港府唔係大膽到逆主而行呀嘛?"},{"pid":"7de925ce77a526daf59a790bf3d9667c574f15d2","tid":2511333,"uid":325838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210315/bkn-20210315080030951-0315_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210315%2Fbkn-20210315080030951-0315_00842_001.html&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=fb6a6c04\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210315/bkn-20210315080030951-0315_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n近日最熱的樓市話題，就是中央發話要香港開始解決房屋問題。如何解決？何時解決？以內地雷厲風行的慣常做法來評估，這次房策新政極有可能在半年內推出，估計將在土地供應重點落墨。事實上，隨着近年樓價愈來愈高，買得起樓的港人愈來愈少，加上樓市供求轉趨平衡，未來若是大量增加住宅供應，樓價下跌是必然結果。"},{"pid":"ab5758a607776ee0d1cd5912c684bc29a361a2ff","tid":2511333,"uid":54326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:29:50.000Z","msg":"香港樓起碼跌50%先叫正常價 但跌5%啲人都狗沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbcd36ac9d53c6d74756bb256a31cdcab512042","tid":2511333,"uid":325838,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ee90d212d677d46678561bee77409b8b7a183c","tid":2511333,"uid":35087,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ab5758a607776ee0d1cd5912c684bc29a361a2ff","tid":2511333,"uid":54326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:29:50.000Z","msg":"香港樓起碼跌50%先叫正常價 但跌5%啲人都狗沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:31:23.000Z","msg":"完全唔值"},{"pid":"5a6d6ef8ad73639ea40b1c52001483a083f21f32","tid":2511333,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:35:32.000Z","msg":"你喺度建議有撚用咩"},{"pid":"95ada68027c1edcf0c454b690b33fda246f6082f","tid":2511333,"uid":306689,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23